---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Contact information for Betting Maths, including current communication status, correction notes and responsible gambling support links."
>
  <section class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Betting Maths is currently a developing educational website. Direct contact details are not published at this stage.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Current status:</strong> There is not currently a public contact email address or contact form for Betting Maths. If that changes, this page will be updated.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Corrections and updates</h2>
    <p>
      Betting Maths aims to keep calculators, examples and explanations clear and useful. However, the site is still being developed and may be updated over time.
    </p>
    <p>
      Users should always check important figures, bookmaker terms, exchange rules and settlement details independently before relying on any calculation.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>What this site can and cannot help with</h2>
    <p>
      Betting Maths explains betting calculations and terminology. It does not provide personal advice, betting tips, predictions, account support or bookmaker customer service.
    </p>

    <table class="contact-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Topic</th>
          <th>Best next step</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Question about a bookmaker account</td>
          <td>Contact the bookmaker directly.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Question about a settled bet</td>
          <td>Check the bookmaker or exchange settlement rules.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Concern about gambling behaviour</td>
          <td>Use the responsible gambling support resources.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>General betting maths concept</td>
          <td>Use the calculators, guides or glossary on this site.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Responsible gambling support</h2>
    <p>
      If betting is causing stress, financial difficulty or loss of control, support is available.
    </p>

    <div class="support-grid">
      <a class="support-card" href="/responsible-gambling/">
        <h3>Responsible Gambling</h3>
        <p>Read safer gambling reminders and support information.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="support-card" href="https://www.gamcare.org.uk/" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <h3>GamCare</h3>
        <p>Access the National Gambling Helpline and gambling support information.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="support-card" href="https://www.gamcare.org.uk/talk/" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <h3>TalkBanStop</h3>
        <p>Find support, blocking tools and self-exclusion information.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Helpline:</strong> In Great Britain, the National Gambling Helpline can be reached on <strong>0808 8020 133</strong>.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Useful site pages</h2>
    <p>
      These pages may answer common questions about the site and its purpose.
    </p>

    <div class="related-grid">
      <a class="related-card" href="/about/">
        <h3>About Betting Maths</h3>
        <p>Learn what the site is for and how it should be used.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="related-card" href="/disclaimer/">
        <h3>Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>Read the educational-use disclaimer and risk notes.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="related-card" href="/privacy-policy/">
        <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>Understand analytics, cookies and future advertising or affiliate wording.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .article-section {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .contact-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .contact-table th,
    .contact-table td {
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .contact-table th {
      color: var(--color-navy);
      background: #f4f7fa;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .contact-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .support-grid,
    .related-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .support-card,
    .related-card {
      display: block;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: var(--color-bg);
    }

    .support-card:hover,
    .related-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(31, 138, 91, 0.45);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .support-card p,
    .related-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--color-muted);
    }

    .article-section a {
      color: var(--color-green-dark);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .support-grid,
      .related-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .support-grid,
      .related-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
